      <header class="hero-section">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="row align-items-center py-4 g-5">
            <div class="col-12 col-md-6">
              <div class="text-center text-md-start">
                <h1 class="display-md-2 display-4 fw-bold text-dark pb-2">
                  <span class="text-primary">Empower </span> Your Future with
                  Freelance Opportunities
                </h1>
                <p class="lead">
                  Unlock your potential as a student! Find exciting assignments,
                  showcase your skills, and start earning today.
                </p>
                <button
                  class="btn btn-primary px-5 py-3 mt-3 fs-5 fw-medium"
                  type="button"
                >
                  Get Started
                </button>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-12 col-md-6">
              <img
                src="assets/hero.webp"
                class="img-fluid"
                alt="a student exploring freelance opportunities"
              />
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </header>
    </div>

    <div class="container">
      <div class="row align-items-center gx-3 gy-5 py-5 mt-5">
        <div class="col-12 col-md-12 col-lg-5">
          <img
            src="assets/img-1.webp"
            class="img-fluid mx-auto d-block"
            alt="a freelancer working on a project"
          />
        </div>
        <div class="col-12 col-md-12 text-center text-lg-start col-lg-7">
          <h2 class="fw-bold text-primary fs-1 pb-3">
            About Freelancer Connect
          </h2>
          <p class="about-text">
            Freelancer Connect is a groundbreaking platform designed
            specifically for students. Itâ€™s a place where you can leverage your
            academic knowledge, creativity, and technical skills to connect with
            clients looking for help on a variety of projects. Whether you're
            looking to make extra money, build your portfolio, or gain
            real-world experience, Freelancer Connect offers endless
            possibilities.
          </p>
          <p class="about-text">
            Our mission is simple: to empower students by providing a secure,
            efficient, and user-friendly platform where you can work as
            freelancers, offer your services, and receive fair compensation. No
            matter what your skillset, Freelancer Connect helps you unlock the
            opportunity to work on assignments that matter.
          </p>
          <button
            class="btn btn-primary px-5 py-3 mt-3 fs-5 fw-medium"
            type="button"
          >
            Explore More
          </button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="features-section py-5">
      <div class="container">
        <h2 class="fs-1 fw-bold text-center pt-5 pb-5 text-primary">
          Why Choose Freelancer Connect?
        </h2>
        <div class="row g-5 pb-5">
          <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
            <div class="card px-3 py-4 shadow-sm">
              <ion-icon class="ionicons" name="bulb-outline"></ion-icon>
              <h3 class="f5">Access Diverse Opportunities</h3>
              <p class="card-text lead">
                Explore a wide range of assignments, from creative writing to
                programming, offering something for every skillset.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
            <div class="card px-3 py-4 shadow-sm blue-bg">
              <ion-icon
                class="ionicons"
                name="shield-checkmark-outline"
              ></ion-icon>
              <h3 class="f5">Build Your Professional Profile</h3>
              <p class="card-text lead">
                Showcase your talents through detailed profiles and portfolios,
                so clients can easily evaluate your work.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4 offset-md-3 offset-0 offset-lg-0">
            <div class="card px-3 py-4 shadow-sm">
              <ion-icon class="ionicons" name="hourglass-outline"></ion-icon>
              <h3 class="f5">Flexible & Timely Projects</h3>
              <p class="card-text lead">
                Choose projects that fit into your schedule and complete them
                within your desired timelines.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="container my-5">
      <div class="row align-items-center justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-12">
          <h2 class="fs-1 fw-bold text-primary text-center pb-5">
            How Freelancer Connect Works
          </h2>
          <ul
            class="nav nav-tabs d-flex flx-wrap justify-content-center"
            id="myTab"
            role="tablist"
          >
            <li class="nav-item" role="presentation">
              <button
                class="nav-link active me-md-3 me-1 text-dark"
                id="home-tab"
                data-bs-toggle="tab"
                data-bs-target="#home-tab-pane"
                type="button"
                role="tab"
                aria-controls="home-tab-pane"
                aria-selected="true"
              >
                For Clients
              </button>
            </li>
            <li class="nav-item" role="presentation">
              <button
                class="nav-link me-md-3 me-1 text-dark"
                id="worker-tab"
                data-bs-toggle="tab"
                data-bs-target="#worker-tab-pane"
                type="button"
                role="tab"
                aria-controls="worker-tab-pane"
                aria-selected="false"
              >
                For Workers
              </button>
            </li>
          </ul>
          <div class="tab-content" id="myTabContent">
            <div
              class="tab-pane fade show active"
              id="home-tab-pane"
              role="tabpanel"
              aria-labelledby="home-tab"
              tabindex="0"
            >
              <div
                class="row g-4 mt-5 justify-content-center align-items-center"
              >
                <div class="col-12 col-md-4">
                  <img
                    src="assets/studentPressure.jpeg"
                    alt=""
                    class="img-fluid d-block mx-auto"
                  />
                </div>
                <div class="col-12 col-md-4">
                  <img
                    src="assets/studentPressure.jpeg"
                    alt=""
                    class="img-fluid d-block mx-auto"
                  />
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div
              class="tab-pane fade"
              id="worker-tab-pane"
              role="tabpanel"
              aria-labelledby="worker-tab"
              tabindex="0"
            >
              <div class="row mt-5 g-4">
                <div class="col-12 col-md-4">
                  <img src="assets/worker-1.webp" alt="" class="img-fluid" />
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="container py-5 mb-5">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-12">
          <h2 class="fw-bold text-primary fs-1 pb-3 text-center">
            Frequently Asked Questions
          </h2>

          <div class="accordion" id="accordionExample">
            <div class="accordion-item">
              <h2 class="accordion-header">
                <button
                  class="accordion-button fs-3 text-dark fw-medium"
                  type="button"
                  data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                  data-bs-target="#collapseOne"
                  aria-expanded="true"
                  aria-controls="collapseOne"
                >
                  How do I post a project as a client?
                </button>
              </h2>
              <div
                id="collapseOne"
                class="accordion-collapse collapse show"
                data-bs-parent="#accordionExample"
              >
                <div class="accordion-body">
                  <p class="lead">
                    Simply create your account, log in, and navigate to the
                    "Post Project" section. Provide a brief description of the
                    task, set a budget, and wait for freelancers to send their
                    offers.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="accordion-item">
              <h2 class="accordion-header">
                <button
                  class="accordion-button collapsed fs-3 text-dark fw-medium"
                  type="button"
                  data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                  data-bs-target="#collapseTwo"
                  aria-expanded="false"
                  aria-controls="collapseTwo"
                >
                  How can I become a worker on Freelancer Connect?
                </button>
              </h2>
              <div
                id="collapseTwo"
                class="accordion-collapse collapse"
                data-bs-parent="#accordionExample"
              >
                <div class="accordion-body">
                  <p class="lead">
                    Sign up, create a professional profile showcasing your
                    skills, and start browsing projects that match your
                    expertise. You can send offers, negotiate with clients, and
                    begin earning.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

